---
title: Baked Chipotle Lentil and Shrimp Taquitos  with Avocado Crema and Tomato Salsa
description: These baked lentil taquitos are packed with veggie and shrimp filling and flavours. Topped off with a limey guacamole and juicy tomatoes, these will quell all cravings!
